pull_request.title: Replace underscores in ciphersuite names with hyphens
pull_request.body:
OpenSSL's rule string code doesn't support selecting ciphersuites with
underscores in their names. See ssl_cipher_process_rulestr in ssl_ciph.c;
while statement at line 1248 will cause the reading of the ciphersuite to
terminate early and look for a truncated version of the name, which will
never be found.

This breaks specifically selecting the ciphersuites by calling SSL_CTX_set_cipher_list.

repo.name: openssl
repo.description: Fork of OpenSSL that includes quantum-resistant algorithms and ciphersuites based on liboqs.
